==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Middle voice from [[όρχος]] orchos (a row or ring); 

===Pronunciation===
*ὀρχέομαι / orcheomai / or-kheh'-om-ahee

===Verb===
'''ὀρχέομαι'''

# to dance (from the ranklike or regular motion): - [[dance]].

